author: kentam
msg: Fix BEEHIVE-850 (Interceptor infrastructure broken when used on overloaded control methods):
Interceptor field naming convention now includes method order index to support overloaded operations (this was being done for events but not for operations).  Added a code-gen DRT.

author: mbo
msg: - Change query20 dependency from api11 to api20.
- The goal is to allow compiling query20 against api20,
not to implement the JDO2 added methods in the Query interface.
The new methods all throw an UnsupportedOperationException.
